description: Deletes the specified virtual tape. This operation is only supported in the tape gateway type.

parameters.name: GatewayARN
parameters.description: The unique Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the gateway that the virtual tape to delete is associated with. Use the  ListGateways operation to return a list of gateways for your account and Amazon Web Services Region.

parameters.name: TapeARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the virtual tape to delete.

nested_items.name: TapeARN
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the deleted virtual tape.
